ast.name: InstantPhotoshop
ast.comment: First select a background photo. Then select the size of a hole to be made in it. Then tap where the hole will be. Now save it. Repeat as desired. Then you can select one of these backgrounds and then go on to take a live photo, typically of a friend's face in the "hole". Their face will appear in whatever background you created.

body.text: NB!!! You are not allowed to blend a photo which is a record!! (At least not if you got it from camera->preview
make sure result is same size as mask
board just chooses its own dimensions
